{
  "id": "64f32f614f819b001c6c22f5",
  "title": "解決の努力が問題の一部になるサーキュラーな問題",
  "created": 1693658981,
  "updated": 1775485479,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "64f32f614f819b001c6c22f5",
      "text": "解決の努力が問題の一部になるサーキュラーな問題",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1693658981,
      "updated": 1693658981
    },
    {
      "id": "64f32f64ed60e60000334530",
      "text": "[トートロジカルコスト][. [/sta/トートロジカルコスト]]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1693658981,
      "updated": 1693659029
    },
    {
      "id": "64f3306ee6003500004864b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1693659246,
      "updated": 1693659246
    },
    {
      "id": "64f330cfe6003500004864bd",
      "text": "[●●するための●●がない]",
      "userId": "65b91ba0863c690027c9ec6a",
      "created": 1693659344,
      "updated": 1712553620
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b542000000000009439d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482179,
      "updated": 1775482179
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b57f00000000000943a0",
      "text": "[考えを進めることが良くないタイプの思索]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482240,
      "updated": 1775482241
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b542000000000009439e",
      "text": "[考えると何かダメになること]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482179,
      "updated": 1775482180
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b6bc00000000000943a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482557,
      "updated": 1775482557
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b75b00000000000943aa",
      "text": "例",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482716,
      "updated": 1775482717
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b7b900000000000943ae",
      "text": " [シロクマ実験]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482810,
      "updated": 1775482810
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3bac500000000000943b6",
      "text": " [底なし沼]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775483590,
      "updated": 1775483590
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b75d00000000000943ab",
      "text": " [不眠症]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482718,
      "updated": 1775482724
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b95300000000000943b0",
      "text": " [パニック障害]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775483220,
      "updated": 1775483220
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b95400000000000943b1",
      "text": " [強迫性障害]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775483221,
      "updated": 1775483226
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b76500000000000943ad",
      "text": " [社交不安障害]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482725,
      "updated": 1775482731
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b75e00000000000943ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482718,
      "updated": 1775482718
    },
    {
      "id": "64f330c3e6003500004864bb",
      "text": "[再帰]/[再帰的]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1693659332,
      "updated": 1693659343
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3b6b700000000000943a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1775482552,
      "updated": 1775482552
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c2260000000000e59c4c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485479,
      "updated": 1775485479
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c1530000000000e59c44",
      "text": "サーキュラーか？[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485267,
      "updated": 1775485272
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c1580000000000e59c46",
      "text": "\t循環参照の英語を調べてみよう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485273,
      "updated": 1775485351
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c1a70000000000e59c47",
      "text": " \tCircular reference",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485351,
      "updated": 1775485353
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c1a90000000000e59c48",
      "text": " サーキュラーだったわ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485354,
      "updated": 1775485358
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c1c50000000000e59c49",
      "text": " recurrent かと思って呟いたが、 recurrent と circular の違いは何だろう？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485381,
      "updated": 1775485427
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c1f30000000000e59c4a",
      "text": " \trecurrent は終わりが来る（来ても良い）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485427,
      "updated": 1775485451
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c20b0000000000e59c4b",
      "text": " \tcircular は終わらずに元の位置まで戻って来る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485452,
      "updated": 1775485469
    },
    {
      "id": "69d3c1540000000000e59c45",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1775485268,
      "updated": 1775485268
    }
  ]
}